io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.entity

Class EntityPlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.VLCVideoPlayer
      • io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.entity.EntityPlayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VideoPlayerContext

    public class EntityPlayer
extends VLCVideoPlayer
    A VLCJ integrated player used to play videos in Minecraft. The library uses a callback for the specific function from native libraries. It renders it on entities.
